      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 38,
      "message": "instead of deleting NetworkResponseCommon and NetwokResponseRequest and introducing new class, I would suggest to abstract out single abstract class.\n\nHere, as per my understanding these two classes signifies request and response.\n\nIn suggested change we need to modify the change in all the files.",
